# local development

## Initial Setup

```
# Create Gemfile
> bundle init

# Edit Gemfile
> vi Gemfile
# Add followings
gem 'jekyll', '3.8.5'
gem "github-pages", group: :jekyll_plugins

# Install bundles
> bundle install --path vendor/bundle
```


## Dev

```
> bundle exec jekyll serve
```

To enable disqus: add `JEKYLL_ENV=production`
